{"id": 795, "genre": 1001, "title": "你收到过什么让你印象深刻的情人节礼物？", "description": "不得不说，有时候我还挺爱我对象/前任的扑朔迷离的品味。（题图来自：KELSEY DAKE）", "record_count": 2615, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183510JtjDk0GMThf5ENKv.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-14T10:29:18Z", "options": [{"id": 50436, "content": "补回一到十八岁生日礼物", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462099}, {"id": 50181, "content": "两包真空包装鸭舌！", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471276}, {"id": 50182, "content": "好几年", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471314}, {"id": 50183, "content": "礼物就是:被秀一脸。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 111687}, {"id": 175880, "content": "一把瑞士军刀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810055}, {"id": 50185, "content": "被爽约?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471012}, {"id": 50186, "content": "情人节有情人的节日", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471356}, {"id": 51211, "content": "单身狗  情人节最特别的礼物?就是看一群人在街上秀恩爱?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478494}, {"id": 50188, "content": "收到了情侣们的会心一击。", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346520}, {"id": 52236, "content": "一个巨大的紫色的熊，这辈子没见过那么丑的熊，他说有白的棕的，然后他挑了最少女的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484118}, {"id": 50189, "content": "情人节是什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471438}, {"id": 50190, "content": "竟然忘了今天是情人节！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 221323}, {"id": 50191, "content": "只收到过一次 就是那种一盒子特别难吃的巧克力配一只特别丑的熊", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5423}, {"id": 51215, "content": "一个hellokitty盒子，里面是4颗真费列罗和5个假费列罗，假的里面是套套。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478706}, {"id": 50192, "content": "。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160433}, {"id": 51216, "content": "一个hellokitty盒子，里面是4颗真费列罗和5个假费列罗，假的里面是套套。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478706}, {"id": 50193, "content": "汽油和火把", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 434721}, {"id": 50194, "content": "鸽子?", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251899}, {"id": 51730, "content": "情人节有礼物吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 470890}, {"id": 50195, "content": "深深的一个吻", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471340}, {"id": 50196, "content": "没有礼物，呵呵哒", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451213}, {"id": 51222, "content": "他从加拿大提前回来陪我过节", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 478758}, {"id": 50199, "content": "今天送了一束玫瑰?，想着跟她说他是我的唯一，但是我还没说，她说玫瑰还行，然后全过程他都是一个字回复，谁能告诉我我是否持续此恋情呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164969}, {"id": 50201, "content": "熊猫猪", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471560}, {"id": 54041, "content": "一群人在我面前发闪光弹。虽然平时也会这么做。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492651}, {"id": 50202, "content": "小白熊机器人", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471560}, {"id": 50203, "content": "狗粮+N", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471493}, {"id": 50204, "content": "轻松小熊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471560}, {"id": 50205, "content": "什么情人节?情人节能吃吗???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433444}, {"id": 50461, "content": "女朋友送我一整套乐高星球大战(丹麦→中国的!!!)", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 472324}, {"id": 50206, "content": "刚收到的，一句情人节快乐就没有了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 246931}, {"id": 50207, "content": "期待着第一份", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 448896}, {"id": 50208, "content": "没收到过不悲哀，悲哀的是从没送出去过！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 189578}, {"id": 50210, "content": "什么是情人节？?", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471638}, {"id": 50211, "content": "好像只有过巧克力吧，方圆五六年里好像没有收过礼物，太遥远了。和男票票放假就异地了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471639}, {"id": 50212, "content": "情人节和我没有关系…", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 471647}, {"id": 50468, "content": "情人节直接被她略过了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473821}, {"id": 50213, "content": "狗粮", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 443089}, {"id": 50214, "content": "男票的亲切问候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 470221}, {"id": 50218, "content": "/微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 463776}, {"id": 50221, "content": "一看到好奇心日报今天还在推送 我心里就好受一些了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 229103}, {"id": 50735, "content": "女朋友的分手", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475425}, {"id": 52527, "content": "右手 或者 左手", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485709}, {"id": 53039, "content": "内存条", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487290}, {"id": 50225, "content": "cosplay情趣装", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 344128}, {"id": 50226, "content": "心爱的人的一句祝福", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 30